How to Play Shell Shockers:-

Enter the game and set a name for your egg character. Choose costumes and weapons. Log in to the game by choosing a server. Use your arrow keys to move and shoot. Throw a bomb with the Q key. Collect bombs around and kill your opponents on the map. Do not forget to buy the golden spatula. Change your team and start the game again.
